# No Co-authored-by or agent branding

Never add `Co-authored-by:` or any Cursor, cursor-agent, or agent branding to git commits or any output. No advertising, ever.

## Commits

- Do not add `Co-authored-by:` (or similar attribution trailers) to commit messages.
- Do not credit or name Cursor, Cursor Agent, or other assistants in commits.

## Other output

- Do not inject tool, IDE, or assistant branding into user-facing text, docs, or generated content unless the user explicitly asked for it.
